# Simulation Environment Diagram

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    A[Simulation Environment] --> B[Physics Engine]
    A --> C[Robot Model]
    A --> D[Environment Model]
    A --> E[Sensor Simulation]
    A --> F[Control Interface]

    B --> B1[PyBullet]
    B --> B2[ODE]
    B --> B3[Mujoco]

    C --> C1[URDF Model]
    C --> C2[Joint Definitions]
    C --> C3[Link Properties]

    D --> D1[Objects]
    D --> D2[Terrain]
    D --> D3[Lighting]

    E --> E1[Camera Sensors]
    E --> E2[LIDAR Sensors]
    E --> E3[IMU Sensors]

    F --> F1[ROS Bridge]
    F --> F2[API Interface]
    F --> F3[Real-time Control]
```

## Simulation Loop

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Controller
    participant S as Simulator
    participant R as Robot Model

    C->>S: Send Commands
    S->>R: Apply Forces/Torques
    R->>S: Update State
    S->>C: Return Sensor Data
    Note over C,S: Repeat at fixed time intervals
```